Package: trialsimulation
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Simulating Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2021-4-1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Matt", "Psioda", email = "matt_psioda@unc.edu", role = "cre"),
    person("Jiawei", "Xu", email = "jiawei@live.unc.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Vincent", "Toups", email = "toups@email.unc.edu", role = "aut"))    
Maintainer: Matt Psioda <matt_psioda@unc.edu>                   
Description: An implementation of the Bayesian anaylsis with historical data incorporated using a normal power prior. 
    Contains a user-friendly wrapper for simulating trials with 2 normally distributed treatment arms  
    and analyzing them using Gibbs sampling under skeptical and enthusiastic priors.
